  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 8 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 24 | <b>Successes:</b> 7</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 12 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 28</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique must be used after successfully knocking a target into the air with Kage Buyou and following them up into the air. Make an unarmed Full Attack against the target, each of which deals an additional die of damage on hit (not multiplied on critical hits). The critical threat range of these attacks is increased by 2. If hit, the target is knocked down to the ground and ends up prone. You will land in a square adjacent to it.<br><br>You will become exhausted for the remainder of the encounter, plus 5 minutes afterwards. A Fortitude save (DC 21) allows you to be fatigued instead. In addition, you suffer 1d4 temporary Strength damage for 1 hour.</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
